Primary reason you did not vote for Labour in #GE2019?
(asked to 2017 Labour voters who did not vote Labour in 2019):

The Leadership: 35%
Brexit: 19%
Policy: 16%
Tactical voting :10%
Extremism: 3%
Didn't get around to voting: 5%

via @YouGov, 13 - 17 Dec
